" Vimium configuration using Colemak
" Not autoloaded, you need to paste in chrome options
" Link hints esntiroahd
unmapAll

" Navigation
map e scrollDown
map u scrollUp
map n scrollLeft
map i scrollRight
map E scrollPageDown
map U scrollPageUp
map r reload
map f linkHints.activateMode
map F linkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map b activateBookmarkFindMode
map B activateBookmarkFindModeToOpenInNewTab

" Using Find
map / enterFindMode
map k performFind
map K performBackwardsFind

" Navigating history
map N goBack
map I goForward

" Manipulating tabs
map y nextTab
map l previousTab
map t createTab
map x removeTab
map z restoreTab

" Miscellaneous
map ? showHelp